dashboard_elements.note_text: List of the top referral domains and the related number of assets downloaded and the percentage of the overall downloads. A referral domain is the URL identifying the web link used to direct users to a web page. The referrer URL can be used to identify the website, search engine, etc. from which users land on the website/web page of interest in the report. It is possible to have a null value for referrer as Web Browsers don’t require Referrer information.

dashboard_elements.note_text: List of the top failed assets that were downloaded including the number of failed downloads and the percentage of the overall failed downloads. dashboard_elements.body_text:
A referrer is the URL identifying the web link used to direct users to a web page. The referrer URL can be used to identify the website, search engine, etc. from which users land on the website/web page of interest in the report.

Web Browsers don't require Referrer information, therefore it is possible to have a null value for referrer.
